This is the instraction file of how create REST API step by step

                            STEP - 1

INSTALL NPM PACKAGE USING COMMAND - npm init -y
This will generate the package.json file

                            STEP - 2
INSTALL EXPRESS PACKAGE USING COMMAND - npm i express
This will install express js into the folder

                            STEP - 3
INSTALL NODEMON USING COMMAND - npm i nodemon

                            STEP - 4
CREATE A app.js FILE